snippet: Nine people, all believed to be illegal immigrants, were killed when a van carrying 19 people rolled over in the border town of Palmview, the authorities said Wednesday.
abstract: Nine people, all believed to be illegal immigrants, are killed as a van carrying 19 people rolls over in Palmview, Texas.
lead_paragraph: Nine people, all believed to be illegal immigrants, were killed when a van carrying 19 people rolled over in the border town of Palmview, the authorities said Wednesday.
